 />\n<br />\n無論邊種情況都好，都幾肯定話黃牛狗蝕硬果啲人係幾無腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04faa7d79a22bb6320a6d4c98b705f371698e875","tid":962834,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcR4oUY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcR4oUY.jpg&h=3fd1f9a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e67bbc2f14259410a856cde982b5c5981f6507b","tid":962834,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45d16b9efdfba1b00ad0e358061af411cc5329bc","tid":962834,"uid":202464,"like":329,"dislike":2,"score":327,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T08:01:24.000Z","msg":"班支那人中晒伏，個個超高黃牛價買飛。但主辦單位原價退錢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"黃牛有得退<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bca6107cc0fd991ea07b1363d79c85d488b50f","tid":962834,"uid":13739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:11:35.000Z","msg":"用2億教訓買黃牛的人！"},{"pid":"b19258651b5262ef84170e28f243d3437cd3cd4c","tid":962834,"uid":8605,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"佢喉唔喉嚨痛唱歌都冇特別好聽<br />\n入去聽演唱會都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f87f4411d52736977da2c9b1dff5a325e8bbcb7","tid":962834,"uid":49830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee77bfb3abad7b0cd0330f16a7e761a9678e738b","tid":962834,"uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T10:17:13.000Z","msg":"90年代到依家2018年<br />\n我估佢身家少極都10億8億流動資金<br />\n仲未計物業私樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16:31:33.000Z","msg":"佢有好多bvi 公司做投資，剩係我見過的公司，都有3-4億portfolio"},{"pid":"192e6788824b6b2485fd2382bbd53e81fc924e8a","tid":962834,"uid":189336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T16: